The paper discusses the practical applications of multi-armed bandits, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also mentions applications in recommender systems and information retrieval, which fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of MABs in healthcare and finance, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
